<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('partials/head.ejs') %>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>AI Generated Content</h1>
        </header>
        <hr>

        <%- include('partials/nav.ejs') %>
        <hr><br>

        <main>
            <form action="/ai" method="get">
                <input type="text" name="topic" placeholder="Enter a topic to learn about it" value="<%= topic %>">
                <button type="submit">Go</button>
            </form>

            <section>
                <h2>AI Summary</h2>

                <div class="ai-response">
                    <% if (response) { %>
                        <%- response %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <p>
                            Artificial Intelligence (AI) refers to the simulation of human intelligence in machines that are programmed to think like humans and mimic their actions. 
                            Its core goal is to enable machines to perform cognitive functions such as learning, reasoning, problem-solving, perception, and understanding language.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            At its heart, AI utilizes complex algorithms and vast datasets to identify patterns, make predictions, and inform decisions. Machine learning (ML), 
                            a crucial subset of AI, allows systems to learn from data without explicit programming, often employing neural networks inspired by the human brain. 
                            Deep learning, a further specialization, uses multi-layered neural networks to process intricate data like images and speech, enabling tasks such as 
                            facial recognition and voice assistants.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            AI powers much of our modern world: from virtual assistants (Siri, Alexa) and recommendation engines (Netflix) to self-driving cars, medical diagnosis, 
                            and fraud detection. In industries, it optimizes operations, automates customer service, and accelerates scientific research.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            While offering immense potential to transform economies and improve quality of life, AI also raises significant ethical considerations regarding data 
                            privacy, algorithmic bias, job displacement, and the need for responsible development. It is a rapidly evolving field, continually pushing the 
                            boundaries of machine capabilities and reshaping our future.
                        </p>

                        <hr>
                        <p>Here are a few links for further research:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <strong>IBM - What is Artificial Intelligence (AI)?</strong><br>
                                <a href="https://www.ibm.com/cloud/learn/what-is-artificial-intelligence">https://www.ibm.com/cloud/learn/what-is-artificial-intelligence</a><br>
                                A good introductory overview from a major tech company, covering definitions, types, and applications.
                            </li>
                            <br>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Wikipedia - Artificial intelligence</strong><br>
                                <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_intelligence">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_intelligence</a><br>
                                A comprehensive starting point for historical context, subfields, philosophy, and future implications.
                            </li>
                            <br>
                            <li>
                                <strong>MIT Technology Review - AI Section</strong><br>
                                <a href="https://news.mit.edu/topic/artificial-intelligence">https://news.mit.edu/topic/artificial-intelligence</a><br>
                                Offers current news, in-depth analysis, and research findings on AI from a leading technology publication.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <hr>
        <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
    </body>
</html>